snippet.title: GOLD PICKER - TRAILER
snippet.description:
In Gold Picker, delve into the world of mining to climb the ranks and collect exceptional ores.

Click like never before!

The primary goal? Accumulate gold... With this precious resource, upgrade your tools, trade them for points, or challenge your friends (in an upcoming update). While exploring the depths, you may encounter unexpected nuggets or unearth geodes.

Treasure Geodes!

Geodes hold hidden treasures: new picks or rare ores. Collect them all to unlock incredible rewards.

Events to make your pick tremble!

Throughout the year, participate in temporary events alone or with your friends. There are exceptional prizes to be won.

Many more updates to come!

Gold Picker will be regularly updated and will remain completely free.
